---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Heidi Blondin, Female Certified Financial Planner"
  description="Are you looking for honest, and holistic financial planning advice? Heidi Blondin Financial is locally owned an operated by women who genuinely care."
>

  <!-- Why us? -->
  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-8" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Why us?</h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          <p>For some of us, thinking about and talking about money is intimidating and stressful. After all, you probably didn't learn about making a budget or doing your taxes in school!</p>
          <p>You may have big questions, like when can I retire? Or how will my family cope if we experience a big change? Is now the time to invest and, if so, into what?</p>
          <p>Our team is passionate about helping families eliminate debt, protect their loved ones and live the retirement of their dreams.</p>
          <p>When you meet with us, we map out your current situation and develop goals and strategies which will accelerate your financial success. We look at the big picture and create a straightforward approach that helps you create peace of mind. Heidi Blondin Financial is locally owned and operated by women who genuinely care about their clients.</p>
          <p>When you're ready, please <a href="/contact/" class="text-brand-plum underline underline-offset-2">connect with us</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Heidi's bio -->
  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/team/heidi-portrait.jpg"
            alt="Female Certified financial planner Kingston Ontario Financial Advisor Retirement Planning Insurance Broker"
            class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover object-top"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="lg:pt-4">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-2" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">
            Heidi Blondin, BA, CFP®, EPC
          </h2>
          <p class="eyebrow-sage mb-6">Certified Financial Planner</p>
          <div class="space-y-5 font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Heidi believes that everyone should have access to the expert help they need. You deserve to work with someone that is knowledgeable, dedicated and passionate about guiding clients to live their best life. Heidi has worked in the financial services sector since 2007, and founded her own firm in 2013 to bring something she felt was missing from the financial planning sector: a focus on what's best for the client.</p>
            <p>Heidi graduated from Queen's University with a Bachelor of Arts in Economics and is qualified to offer both Mutual Fund and Life Insurance Solutions. She holds her Certified Financial Planning designation as well as her Elder Planning Counselor designation.</p>
            <p>Heidi regularly attends industry training sessions and conferences to further enhance her financial knowledge and resources.</p>
            <p>Mutual funds are offered through Investia Financial Services Inc.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team grid -->
  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Heidi's Team</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">

        <!-- Angela McCann -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/angela/">
            <img
              src="/team/angela-portrait.jpg"
              alt="Angela McCann"
              class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top mb-4"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </a>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Angela McCann</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Licensed Assistant</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Joanne Charron -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/joanne/">
            <img
              src="/team/joanne-portrait.jpg"
              alt="Joanne Charron - Insurance Advisor"
              class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top mb-4"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </a>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Joanne Charron</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Insurance Advisor</p>
        </div>

        <!-- John Blondin -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <img
            src="/team/john-portrait.jpg"
            alt="About John Blondin - Operations Manager"
            class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top mb-4"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p class="font-serif text-lg text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">John Blondin</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Operations Manager</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Jack Blondin -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/jack/">
            <img
              src="/team/jack-portrait.jpg"
              alt="Jack Blondin Headshot"
              class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top mb-4"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </a>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Jack Blondin</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Assistant</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
